{
  "stem": "18802.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 27.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In one of the main streets of Tel Aviv that would be compared to market like it was 20 years ago, yeah, not the market of [INAUDIBLE] of today.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was a store in the best neighborhood who sold typewriters.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he had a typewriter, one typewriter, in a big showcase.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I met this guy at the party.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I said to him, Klaus, you are really a fool.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You have one typewriter in a big showcase.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You pay a girl to take your orders.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He lived mostly off repairs, yeah?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So you have one girl there who take orders by telephone, yeah?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's a foolish idea.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I give you an offer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I pay half your rent.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You give me your showcase.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I take your orders.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And you don't need the girl.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He said, could you start tomorrow?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] I said, not tomorrow, but on, on Monday.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So, I got a beautiful place.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Now, he told-- he asked me, what would you sell?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I said, I have an idea.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "In Israel-- that means it was still Palestine, there is the habit whenever you are invited, you never come with empty hands.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And whatever you bring-- a piece of chocolate or a book or a flowers-- it's like a prize stamp on it, yeah?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I would like to open a store for [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "That means little gifts, yeah?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I will have different things.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I think I will make bookkeeping what sells best.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And after two months, I will make this what only sells best.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And so I started.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And it was really hard to find merchandise, yes?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But I had a few pounds from them from the sale of, of our furniture and our household goods.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I really started this business.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I decorated nicely.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
